page.title: 08SPORT IN WARBOYS 3
page.content: {HEALTH CLUB} The Warboys{Health Club}is held at the school on Monday and Thursday afternoon.It costs three pounds for a year and has thirty members. {SPORTS AND SOCIAL CLUB The club has been running for one hundred years.It has three hundred and seventy five members.The club is open every day except Monday. {WARBOYS TOWN FOOTBALL CLUB} The club consists of five teams,the first team,the reserves,the U16 team and two youth teams.The club has been running for 100 years next season.There are matches every Saturday (in season).They are in the Peterborough Premier League. {NETBALL CLUB There are 25 members in two teams.The club has been running for 8 years and Monday is pracice night.
